        "protagonistas":"Juliette",
        "sinopsis":"El miedo aprenderá a temerme.<br>El Punto Omega ha sido destruido y Juliette no sabe qué ha pasado con sus amigos. También desconoce si ahora ella es la única capaz de acabar con el Restablecimiento. Pero para hacerlo tendrá que apoyarse en la última persona en la que pensó que confiaría: Warner, el hijo del líder del Restablecimiento.<br>Con la incertidumbre de si los rebeldes, entre los que se encuentra Adam, siguen vivos, Juliette tendrá que aceptar por fin su don si quiere detener la guerra de una vez por todas.<br>El final está cada vez más cerca y ha llegado la hora de tomar las grandes decisiones. ¿A qué bando pertenece? ¿En quién va a confiar? Y sobre todo, ¿a quién va a amar?",
        "cita":"“Words, I think, are such unpredictable creatures.<br>No gun, no sword, no army or king will ever be more powerful than a sentence. Swords may cut and kill, but words will stab and stay, burying themselves in our bones to become corpses we carry into the future, all the time digging and failing to rip their skeletons from our flesh.”<br><br>“Ignite, my love. Ignite.”<br><br>“Why do you call her 'love'?” James asks. “I've heard you say that before, too. A lot. Are you in love with her? I think Adam's in love with her. Kenji's not in love with her, though. I already asked him.”<br>Warner blinks at him.<br>“Well?” James asks.<br>“Well what?”<br>“Are you in love with her?”<br>“Are you in love with her?”<br>“What?” James blushes. “No. She's like a million years older than me.”<br>“Would anyone else like to take over this conversation?” Warner asks, looking around the group.”<br><br>“The tattoo is just setting below his hp bone.<br>H e l l i s e m p t y<br>a n d a l l t h e d e v i l s a r e h e r e<br>I kiss my way across the words.<br>Kissing away the devils.<br>Kissing away the pain.”<br><br>“Aaron Warner Anderson, chief commander and regent of Sector 45, son of the supreme commander of The Reestablishment.<br>He has a soft spot for fashion.”",
